Quote: <i>About `Sun Dogs'.</i> And mention of [Charles] Douglas ... recalls a curious theory he propounded ... when we were discussing meteorological phenomena of the high Alps, and in particular the `sun dog', that luminous coloured halo produced by the sun's rays shining through a damp and vaporous atmosphere.
